    "summary": "Chrome Policy exposes one authenticated REST API at `https://chromepolicy.googleapis.com/` for managing Chrome/ChromeOS policies, authenticated with Google OAuth 2.0 user or service-account access tokens.",
    "description": "Chrome Policy API lets Google Workspace administrators programmatically view and manage Chrome browser and ChromeOS device policies for their organization. It complements Google Admin console and related Admin SDK APIs for enterprise Chrome management.",
